	<help>Maximum allowable Recurrence Time in Paypal :&lt;br/&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;D – for days allowable range  is 1 to 90&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;W – for weeks allowable range is 1 to 52&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;M – for months allowable range is 1 to 24&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Y – for years allowable range is 1 to 5&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
      Number of times that subscription payments recur should be greater than 1 and less than 50, if you set it to 0 it means it will charge for forever, until cancellation.
      <![CDATA[
